========================================================================
Enzo: INSTALL
========================================================================

1. First, Enzo currently (as of v1_0_0-pre1) assumes MakeMacros is in
   your home directory.  If you don't have MakeMacros in your home
   directory, you can use "ln -s" to make a symbolic link in your home
   directory from Enzo/MakeMacros.

...

